Package dao

Interface IPrimaryEntityDAO<T>

Type Parameters:
T - A generic type enabling sub-type polymorphism.
All Superinterfaces:
IGenericEntity
All Known Implementing Classes:
CustomerDAOImpl, OrderDAOImpl, ProductDAOImpl, SupplierDAOImpl
public interface IPrimaryEntityDAO<T> extends IGenericEntity
The IPrimaryEntityDAO interface provides the CRUD method definitions for primary entities. It inherits a TIMEOUT metric from the IGenericEntity interface.
